ike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T08:40:22.000Z","msg":"民主建港聯盟"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T08:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20140725/s00046/1406285108109_FA2F407020B7F91262765E67CCE36616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20140725%2Fs00046%2F1406285108109_FA2F407020B7F91262765E67CCE36616.jpg&h=f9a256cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"改名變建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f13c222f5d936b84f60a067ee47c264cd78c66e","tid":2093972,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"681c9fb1a9f616bbd973c6722a859c7a259bfe9b","tid":2093972,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T08:32:51.000Z","msg":"#轉載新聞 #新常識<br />\n#而家香港政府同香港人講法例及常識呀<br />\n#字面 #字底<br />\n<br />\n咁，請問，憑「常識」，<br />\n「解放軍」係咪字面都有「解放」意思？<br />\n「解放軍」係咪字底都有「改變特區法律地位或顛覆國家政權含意」？<br />\n<br />\n//政府在港區國安法實施後，就「光復香港時代革命」口號發聲明指，有港獨、分離、改變特區法律地位或顛覆國家政權含意。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員湯家驊指口號有改變制度意味，相信很多人憑常識會跟政府有一樣解讀，但不認為干犯國安法的人一定終身不可再參選。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/468189090692/posts/10163917964320693/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F468189090692%2Fposts%2F10163917964320693%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=34de7813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/468189090692/posts/10163917964320693/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:19:50.000Z","msg":"佢講咗我一直質疑嘅嘢"},{"pid":"6b143b81df7b9cc882803662bae7a1106228201f","tid":2093972,"uid":201142,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"33f24b395d6a3ef6beeb89fa1353713e22dad0b6","tid":2093972,"uid":32577,"like":156,"dislike":1,"score":155,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"強烈要求改名做自衛軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/n