,"tid":2093972,"uid":34681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdff56e5f21408b789f3cee314ed2fd5ef5ea311","tid":2093972,"uid":201583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"681c9fb1a9f616bbd973c6722a859c7a259bfe9b","tid":2093972,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T08:32:51.000Z","msg":"#轉載新聞 #新常識<br />\n#而家香港政府同香港人講法例及常識呀<br />\n#字面 #字底<br />\n<br />\n咁，請問，憑「常識」，<br />\n「解放軍」係咪字面都有「解放」意思？<br />\n「解放軍」係咪字底都有「改變特區法律地位或顛覆國家政權含意」？<br />\n<br />\n//政府在港區國安法實施後，就「光復香港時代革命」口號發聲明指，有港獨、分離、改變特區法律地位或顛覆國家政權含意。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員湯家驊指口號有改變制度意味，相信很多人憑常識會跟政府有一樣解讀，但不認為干犯國安法的人一定終身不可再參選。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/468189090692/posts/10163917964320693/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F468189090692%2Fposts%2F10163917964320693%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=34de7813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/468189090692/posts/10163917964320693/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"cctai 兒登仔真係好撚幼稚，解放軍嘅（解放）係指中共解放資本主義制度下嘅土地，而家中共都話自己係社會主義，點樣有顛覆國家政權嘅含意？"},{"pid":"b31b734e594a4c24caf8803f6235977837262917","tid":2093972,"uid":354545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"febe012a645a32b4f58363a062aa40134ef36ade","tid":2093972,"uid":43809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0980304a341225beeb6dc6bb9290fec9e8bb6f3","tid":2093972,"uid":1149,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"5e65afcec43e8c58ec2419d016bed6c4e35fd080","tid":2093972,"uid":48851,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T08:40:22.000Z","msg":"民主建港聯盟"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T08:42:15.000