0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T08:32:51.000Z","msg":"#轉載新聞 #新常識<br />\n#而家香港政府同香港人講法例及常識呀<br />\n#字面 #字底<br />\n<br />\n咁，請問，憑「常識」，<br />\n「解放軍」係咪字面都有「解放」意思？<br />\n「解放軍」係咪字底都有「改變特區法律地位或顛覆國家政權含意」？<br />\n<br />\n//政府在港區國安法實施後，就「光復香港時代革命」口號發聲明指，有港獨、分離、改變特區法律地位或顛覆國家政權含意。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員湯家驊指口號有改變制度意味，相信很多人憑常識會跟政府有一樣解讀，但不認為干犯國安法的人一定終身不可再參選。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/468189090692/posts/10163917964320693/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F468189090692%2Fposts%2F10163917964320693%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=34de7813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/468189090692/posts/10163917964320693/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:10:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解放香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"62c0a826d2e8b041fccebfcd56af1537d1d2a61e","tid":2093972,"uid":36531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15dd72374c83297642e512878df79c28dcaa4ad6","tid":2093972,"uid":48357,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8d7e06f7edfb457ece7a43da278362d79fc106a1","tid":2093972,"uid":173326,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T08:41:02.000Z","msg":"解放=free<br />\nfree Hong Kong=解放香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:02:42.000Z","msg":"解放香港<br />\n人民革命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:15:34.000Z","msg":"革命無罪 造反有理"}],"pinned":{"pid":"da81b4bb6ab8719f2fa7552a5ffdbc1dd8377ea6","tid":2093972,"uid":49747,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"民建聯<br />\n民主建港聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gi